{"tid":1806983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家唔好令文宣同標語變成廢紙！！！","createTime":"2020-01-01T14:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T16:16:47.000Z","uid":85603,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c45d6933dc7e5335c5c6700bb3eccd343b422b27","tid":1806983,"uid":85603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"印象中之前有手足開post提過，不過都想提多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次去遊行都見到好多組織派標語俾大家舉，好多手足會拎，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家行完唔好就咁掉左佢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n明白大家可能行完唔知點處置張標語，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>其實我地可以帶返去自己區貼連儂牆！！！</strong></span></strong></span><br />\n咁就唔會浪費左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先返去自己區行過連儂牆，都見到有手足咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地成日笑藍絲集會之後亂咁掉中國國旗，我地都要做返好啲，珍惜自己嘅文宣同標語<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日見到垃圾桶有標語掉左係度，之前去完國際戰線嘅集會見過有美國旗掉左係地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，都有幫手放返係牆上，除左唔想浪費，仲關形象事架，希望大家一齊每人做多少少！！"},{"pid":"64c9af8267ea60f475f027e12aa500ddc988b832","tid":1806983,"uid":101756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"😡"},{"pid":"daf6ba441856668de577547b242a33441e35e57e","tid":1806983,"uid":215760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:01:29.000Z","msg":"同意 見好多人掉 成地都係 我都係儲埋 返去貼連儂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6432dc5a74bfe60cd7ff8d210950343014bdbdfe","tid":1806983,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de6918e885df0bf6f2c95e36b1d8942a9d8ee2e6","tid":1806983,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy